<view class="app-shell">
  <view class="section-card hero-card deletion-hero-card">
    <text class="hero-kicker">不可撤销操作</text>
    <text class="hero-title deletion-hero-title">
      提交后会立即退出登录，并进入 {{deletionWindowDays}} 天待删除窗口。
    </text>
    <text class="hero-body deletion-hero-body">
      冷静期结束后，云端账号、身份绑定、记录、待办和媒体对象会被彻底删除。
    </text>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{isLoadingStatus}}" class="section-card loading-state">
    <view class="loading-spinner"></view>
    <text class="loading-title">正在检查账号状态…</text>
    <text class="loading-body">先确认你的当前账号是否已经提交过注销申请。</text>
  </view>

  <block wx:elif="{{!account.isSignedIn}}">
    <view class="section-card">
      <text class="helper-text">当前还没登录云端账号。登录后，这里才会显示注销入口。</text>
    </view>
  </block>

  <block wx:elif="{{status.status === 'pending'}}">
    <view class="section-card">
      <text class="section-title">账号已提交注销</text>
      <text class="helper-text">{{status.message}}</text>
      <text wx:if="{{scheduledForLabel}}" class="helper-text">预计彻底删除时间：{{scheduledForLabel}}</text>
    </view>
  </block>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="section-card">
      <text class="section-title">确认方式</text>
      <text class="helper-text" wx:if="{{account.hasPhone}}">
        当前账号已绑定手机号 {{account.maskedPhone}}，请先获取注销验证码。
      </text>
      <text class="helper-text" wx:elif="{{account.hasWeChat}}">
        当前账号没有绑定手机号，需要再次完成一次微信授权确认。
      </text>
      <text class="helper-text" wx:else>
        当前账号没有可用的注销确认方式，请联系客服处理。
      </text>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{account.hasPhone}}" class="section-card">
      <view class="cloud-code-row">
        <input
          class="cloud-input cloud-input--code"
          type="number"
          maxlength="6"
          placeholder="输入注销验证码"
          value="{{code}}"
          bindinput="handleCodeInput"
        />
        <button
          class="action-button ghost-button small-button cloud-code-button"
          bindtap="handleSendCode"
          disabled="{{isBusy || sendCountdown > 0}}"
        >
          {{sendCountdown > 0 ? sendCountdown + ' 秒' : '发送验证码'}}
        </button>
      </view>
      <view class="action-row action-row--single">
        <button class="action-button danger-button" bindtap="handleConfirmPhoneDeletion" loading="{{isBusy}}">
          提交注销申请
        </button>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view wx:elif="{{account.hasWeChat}}" class="section-card">
      <text class="helper-text">点击下方按钮后，会再次拉起微信授权，用于确认本次注销申请。</text>
      <view class="action-row action-row--single">
        <button class="action-button danger-button" bindtap="handleConfirmWeChatDeletion" loading="{{isBusy}}">
          使用微信确认注销
        </button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
